      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for someone seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates honest-condition vehicles, but it still offers solid everyday utility and plenty of potential. A smart buy for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone looking for inexpensive mobility without unnecessary frills.",
