      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car that\u2019s ready to be useful? This one isn\u2019t fancy, but it\u2019s an honest driver with plenty of potential for someone who wants affordable wheels, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, it\u2019s a great chance to get into a car without spending big. If you appreciate straightforward value, this could be the one.",
