      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who wants an inexpensive, usable car with good bones and straightforward mechanicals. This one shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but it presents as a complete, running driver with plenty of serviceable life left for a commuter, first car, or light project. Powertrain feels willing, chassis is composed, and it offers a practical platform for someone who values function over flash. Priced accordingly for its condition and ideal for a buyer who knows how to spot value in an honest car.",
